genresAdvancedInfo.name: punk tico
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Punk tico is a subgenre of punk rock that originated in Costa Rica. It features fast-paced, aggressive music with lyrics that reflect the political and social issues of the country. The genre emerged in the 1990s and gained popularity in the early 2000s with bands such as Seka and Gandhi. Punk tico is known for its DIY ethos and anti-establishment attitude.
